-- Turkey's Alternatifbank plans up to $350 mln borrowing abroad
-- 
-- Wed Jun 04, 2014 07:31AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, June 4 (Reuters) - Turkey's Alternatifbank <ALNTF.IS> said on Wednesday it had mandated its head office to look into the possibility of borrowing up to $350 mln from international capital markets through bonds and similar financing instruments.   (Writing by Daren Butler; Editing by Nick Tattersall)  ((daren.butler@thomsonreuters.com)(+90-212-350 7122)(Reuters Messaging: daren.butler.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: ALTERNATIFBANK/

